Insider Activity


Individual




David van Skilling



Mr. David van Skilling is Chairman at Onvia, Inc., Chief Executive Officer at Skilling Enterprises, and Independent Director at American Business Bank. He is on the Board of Directors at American Business Bank.
Mr. van Skilling was previously employed as Lead Director by The First American Corp., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Experian Information Solutions, Inc., and Executive Vice President by TRW, Inc. He also served on the board at Corelogic US, Inc., CoreLogic, Inc., Docufide, Inc., The Lamson & Sessions Co., McData Corp., and Parchment, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Colorado College and an MBA from Pepperdine University.



